OL,3,CUltra-processed foods and alcohol
OL,4,Ccontribute to 2.7m deaths a year, says
OL,5,CWHO
OL,7,FIn a new report, the WHO calls for
OL,8,F"strict regulation to curb industry
OL,9,Fpower" and for governments to drive
OL,10,Fforward health policies which are
OL,11,Fregularly "challenged, delayed,
OL,12,Fweakened or stopped" by industry.
OL,14,FWHO said "more than 7,400 people are
OL,15,Fdying every day" in its European
OL,16,Fregion due to harmful products and
OL,17,Fpractices "driven by commercial
OL,18,Findustry".
