OL,3,CUltra-processed foods and alcohol
OL,4,Ccontribute to 2.7m deaths a year, says
OL,5,CWHO
OL,7,FThese figures do not include deaths
OL,8,Fcaused by obesity, high blood
OL,9,Fpressure, high blood sugar or high
OL,10,Fcholesterol level ` all of which are
OL,11,Flinked to unhealthy diets, it said.
OL,13,FThe report called on governments to
OL,14,Frecognise the tactics used by industry
OL,15,F` such as blaming individuals,
OL,16,Fmarketing, spreading disinformation,
OL,17,Fpromotions on social media, lobbying
OL,18,Fand "subverting science" such as by
OL,19,Ffunding research that promotes their
OL,20,Fgoals.
