OL,4,Ccontribute to 2.7m deaths a year, says
OL,5,CWHO
OL,7,FThe WHO said the "primary interest of
OL,8,Fall major corporations is profit",
OL,9,Fwhile having a large market share
OL,10,F"often also translates into political
OL,11,Fpower".
OL,13,FIt added: "Regardless of the product
OL,14,Fthey sell, their (industry) interests
OL,15,Fdo not align with either public health
OL,16,For the broader public interest.
OL,18,F"Any policy that could impact their
OL,19,Fsales and profits is therefore a
OL,20,Fthreat, and they should play no role
OL,21,Fin the development of that policy.
